Title: Singled Out
Plot: An abandoned car is found full of blood, registered to a missing Navy lieutenant. The NCIS team learns that the missing lieutenant was profiling men, trying to find a perfect man for herself. When they find out that the woman intended to go to a seminar at a local hotel, Ziva goes undercover to find more information. Ducky is busy going through the profiles of the men. Jenny makes a secret offer to Tony.
GuestStars: Seamus Dever, Misha Collins, Claire Coffee, Daniel Hagen, Mike Beaver, Mieko Hillman
